(15, 'com_content.article.5', '', '2022-09-16 10:58:32', 775, 3167, 'c6e5cf3c3c63d498f0d90da8024b064a5c98b4da', '{\"id\":\"5\",\"asset_id\":97,\"title\":\"Blog Article 1\",\"alias\":\"blog\",\"introtext\":\"<p><span id=\\\"p263\\\">Le d\\u00e9l\\u00e9gu\\u00e9 m\\u00e9dical est l\\u2019interm\\u00e9diaire entre le laboratoire et les praticiens du secteur m\\u00e9dical.<\\/span><span id=\\\"p264\\\"> Sa mission principale consiste \\u00e0 assurer la promotion d\\u2019un ou de plusieurs produits fabriqu\\u00e9s par le laboratoire pharmaceutique o\\u00f9 il travaille.<\\/span><br \\/><span id=\\\"p265\\\">Dans cet ordre d\\u2019id\\u00e9es, le d\\u00e9l\\u00e9gu\\u00e9 m\\u00e9dical vise \\u00e0 ce que les professionnels du secteur prescrivent davantage les produits qu\\u2019il repr\\u00e9sente.<\\/span><span id=\\\"p266\\\"> De m\\u00eame, il garantit l\\u2019optimisation des ventes surtout que la concurrence est vive entre les laboratoires.<\\/span><span id=\\\"p267\\\"> \\u00c0 ce titre, le d\\u00e9l\\u00e9gu\\u00e9 m\\u00e9dical planifie et alterne des visites aux m\\u00e9decins, pharmacies d\\u2019officine, chirurgiens-dentistes, \\u2026<\\/span><span id=\\\"p268\\\">.<\\/span><span id=\\\"p269\\\"> Etc.<\\/span><br \\/><span id=\\\"p272\\\">Tout d\\u2019abord, le responsable m\\u00e9dical doit connaitre \\u00e0 c\\u0153ur les produits qu\\u2019il va exposer <span id=\\\"p270\\\">(Efficacit\\u00e9, tol\\u00e9rance, posologie\\u2026<\\/span><span id=\\\"p271\\\"> Etc)<\\/span>.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":8,\"created\":\"2022-09-16 08:29:34\",\"created_by\":\"775\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2022-09-16 10:58:32\",\"modified_by\":775,\"checked_out\":775,\"checked_out_time\":\"2022-09-16 10:55:12\",\"publish_up\":\"2022-09-16 08:29:34\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/two-mature-smiling-doctors-having-260nw-1647340636.webp#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/two-mature-sm